## 📎 File Handling Quick Reference

| Scenario | What to Do | Details |
|----------|------------|---------|
| **User gives AI a file** | Upload to `context/` folder, tell AI to read it | `16-ai-file-input.md` |
| **App needs file upload** | Use memory storage (default) or `/data` for persistence | `14-file-handling.md` |

**`context/` folder is gitignored** - safe for requirements docs, example data, design mockups.

